@page "/features/quality"
@layout Components.Layout.PublicLayout
@attribute [AllowAnonymous]
@attribute [ExcludeFromInteractiveRouting]

@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.Web

<PageTitle>Quality &amp; Compliance - Vectrik</PageTitle>

<!-- Breadcrumb -->
<div class="pub-breadcrumb">
    <a href="/features">Features</a>
    <span class="pub-breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
    <span>Quality &amp; Compliance</span>
</div>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="pub-page-hero">
    <h1 class="pub-gradient-text">Quality &amp; Compliance</h1>
    <p class="pub-page-hero-sub">Inline QC, NCR management, SPC charting, and full powder-to-part traceability &mdash; built to keep you audit-ready without slowing down production.</p>
</section>

<!-- Problem Statement -->
<section class="pub-section">
    <div class="pub-feature-detail">
        <div class="pub-feature-detail-content pub-fade-up">
            <h2 class="pub-section-title">Compliance Without the Paper Trail</h2>
            <p class="pub-about-text">
                Aerospace and defense manufacturers need full traceability for ISO 9001, AS9100, and ITAR. In most AM shops, that means binders full of paper records, manual spreadsheets for quality data, and weeks of preparation before every audit.
            </p>
            <p class="pub-about-text">
                Vectrik captures quality data in the natural flow of production. Operators complete inline inspections as they work. NCRs are logged when defects are discovered. Powder lot genealogy is recorded automatically. When the auditor arrives, everything is already documented.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Inline QC -->
<section class="pub-section pub-section-alt">
    <div class="pub-feature-spotlight pub-fade-up">
        <div class="pub-feature-spotlight-text">
            <div class="pub-feature-spotlight-label">In-Flow Quality</div>
            <h2>Inline QC Checks</h2>
            <p>Embed quality checkpoints at any production stage. Operators complete inspections without breaking their workflow &mdash; no separate quality system to log into.</p>
            <ul class="pub-feature-detail-list">
                <li>Configurable pass/fail criteria per stage and part type</li>
                <li>Dimensional measurement capture with tolerance validation</li>
                <li>Photo documentation for visual inspections</li>
                <li>Automatic hold if a check fails &mdash; part doesn't advance until resolved</li>
                <li>QC history attached to every part for full traceability</li>
                <li>Checklist-style inspections for multi-point checks</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-feature-spotlight-visual">
            <div class="pub-qc-mockup">
                <div class="pub-qc-header">QC Check: Post-CNC Inspection</div>
                <div class="pub-qc-item pub-qc-pass">
                    <span class="pub-qc-status">PASS</span>
                    <span class="pub-qc-name">Surface finish Ra</span>
                    <span class="pub-qc-value">1.2 &mu;m (spec: &le; 1.6)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pub-qc-item pub-qc-pass">
                    <span class="pub-qc-status">PASS</span>
                    <span class="pub-qc-name">OD dimension</span>
                    <span class="pub-qc-value">25.02 mm (spec: 25.00 &plusmn; 0.05)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pub-qc-item pub-qc-fail">
                    <span class="pub-qc-status">FAIL</span>
                    <span class="pub-qc-name">Bore diameter</span>
                    <span class="pub-qc-value">12.08 mm (spec: 12.00 &plusmn; 0.03)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pub-qc-action">Part held &mdash; NCR required</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- NCR Management -->
<section class="pub-section">
    <div class="pub-feature-spotlight pub-feature-spotlight-reverse pub-fade-up">
        <div class="pub-feature-spotlight-text">
            <div class="pub-feature-spotlight-label">Defect Tracking</div>
            <h2>NCR Management</h2>
            <p>When a defect is found, log it immediately. Track non-conformances from discovery through root-cause analysis to corrective action &mdash; with full audit trails.</p>
            <ul class="pub-feature-detail-list">
                <li>One-click NCR creation from a failed QC check</li>
                <li>Link NCRs to specific parts, builds, work orders, and operators</li>
                <li>Root-cause categories: process, material, tooling, operator, design</li>
                <li>Corrective action tracking with due dates and assignments</li>
                <li>Disposition options: rework, scrap, use-as-is, return to vendor</li>
                <li>NCR dashboards showing trends, repeat defects, and closure rates</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-feature-spotlight-visual">
            <div class="pub-ncr-mockup">
                <div class="pub-ncr-header">NCR-2847-003</div>
                <div class="pub-ncr-row">
                    <span class="pub-ncr-label">Part</span>
                    <span>Bracket-A7 (SN: 2847-04)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pub-ncr-row">
                    <span class="pub-ncr-label">Stage</span>
                    <span>Post-CNC Inspection</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pub-ncr-row">
                    <span class="pub-ncr-label">Defect</span>
                    <span>Bore diameter out of tolerance (+0.08 mm)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pub-ncr-row">
                    <span class="pub-ncr-label">Root Cause</span>
                    <span>Tool wear &mdash; boring bar past replacement interval</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pub-ncr-row">
                    <span class="pub-ncr-label">Disposition</span>
                    <span class="pub-ncr-disposition">Rework &mdash; re-bore to spec</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pub-ncr-row">
                    <span class="pub-ncr-label">Status</span>
                    <span class="pub-ncr-status-open">Open &mdash; corrective action in progress</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- SPC & Traceability -->
<section class="pub-section pub-section-alt">
    <h2 class="pub-section-title pub-fade-up">Process Control &amp; Traceability</h2>
    <p class="pub-section-sub pub-fade-up">Catch drift before it becomes a defect. Trace every part back to its source.</p>
    <div class="pub-feature-grid pub-feature-grid-3">
        <div class="pub-card pub-fade-up">
            <div class="pub-card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M4 4v16h16"/>
                    <path d="M4 14l4-4 4 2 4-6 4 4"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="pub-card-title">SPC Charts</h3>
            <p class="pub-card-text">Statistical process control charting tracks critical dimensions over time. Automated control limit calculations (UCL/LCL) and trend alerts flag drift before it causes scrap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-card pub-fade-up">
            <div class="pub-card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 003 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0021 16z"/>
                    <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/>
                    <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="pub-card-title">Powder Lot Genealogy</h3>
            <p class="pub-card-text">Trace any finished part back to its powder lot, including alloy, supplier, certifications, and reuse history. Essential for aerospace and defense traceability requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-card pub-fade-up">
            <div class="pub-card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/>
                    <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
                    <line x1="8" y1="13" x2="16" y2="13"/>
                    <line x1="8" y1="17" x2="16" y2="17"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="pub-card-title">Audit-Ready Records</h3>
            <p class="pub-card-text">Every inspection, NCR, disposition, and corrective action is timestamped and linked to the part. Pull a complete quality history for any part in seconds, not hours.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Compliance Standards -->
<section class="pub-section">
    <h2 class="pub-section-title pub-fade-up">Built for Regulated Manufacturing</h2>
    <div class="pub-compliance-grid pub-fade-up">
        <div class="pub-compliance-card">
            <h4>ISO 9001</h4>
            <p>Quality management system foundation. Document control, process monitoring, corrective actions, and continuous improvement &mdash; all built into daily operations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-compliance-card">
            <h4>AS9100</h4>
            <p>Aerospace-specific quality requirements. Enhanced traceability, configuration management, risk assessment, and first article inspection support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-compliance-card">
            <h4>ITAR</h4>
            <p>International Traffic in Arms Regulations. Enterprise plans include US-only hosting, access controls restricted to US persons, and export-controlled data handling.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-compliance-card">
            <h4>CMMC</h4>
            <p>Cybersecurity Maturity Model Certification. Role-based access controls, encrypted data at rest and in transit, audit logging, and tenant isolation.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Next/Prev Navigation -->
<section class="pub-section pub-section-alt">
    <div class="pub-subpage-nav">
        <div class="pub-subpage-nav-item">
            <a href="/features/shop-floor">
                <span class="pub-subpage-nav-dir">Previous</span>
                <span class="pub-subpage-nav-title">Shop Floor Execution</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-subpage-nav-item">
            <a href="/features/analytics">
                <span class="pub-subpage-nav-dir">Next</span>
                <span class="pub-subpage-nav-title">Analytics &amp; Reporting</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="pub-cta-banner">
    <h2 class="pub-gradient-text">See compliance in action</h2>
    <p>We'll show you inline QC, NCR workflows, and audit-ready traceability in a live demo.</p>
    <a href="/demo" class="pub-btn pub-btn-primary pub-btn-lg">Request a Demo</a>
</section>
